{"lemma":"جُنْدُبٌ","slug":"جُنْدُبٌ","root":"ج.ن.د.ب","root_slug":"ج-ن-د-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ن-د-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n5195","n6462"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8F%D9%86%D9%92%D8%AF%D9%8F%D8%A8%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"grasshopper"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare جَدْجَد (jadjad)."},"ipa":["/d͡ʒun.dub/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n5195","headword_ar":"جُنْدَبٌ","root":"jdb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junodubN","text_ar":"جُنْدُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, &c.) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jinodabN","text_ar":"جِنْدَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dirohamN","text_ar":"دِرْهَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sb, M, K,) the last of which is of weakest authority, because of a rare measure, whereof it has been said that there are only four examples: (TA:) in all of them the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"n","text_ar":"ن"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said by some to be radical; but others, with more reason, hold it to be augmentative: (MF:) Sb says that it is augmentative: (S:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A species of locust,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well known:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"male locust:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small locust:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to Seer,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SadFY","text_ar":"صَدًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a kind of cricket"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that creaks by night, and hops and flies:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[but see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SadFY","text_ar":"صَدًى"},{"kind":"text","text":":] or, accord. to the M, it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smaller than the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SdY","text_ar":"صدى"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and is found in the deserts:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaAdibu","text_ar":"جَنَادِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sr~","text_ar":"صرّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljndb","text_ar":"الجندب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sar~a Aljunodabu","text_ar":"صَرَّ الجُنْدَبُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jndb","text_ar":"جندب"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"creaked"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is a saying of the Arabs, used as a proverb; alluding to a difficult affair by which a person is troubled in mind; originating from the fact that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jndb","text_ar":"جندب"},{"kind":"text","text":", when its feet are scorched by the heated ground, does not keep them steadily upon it, and a creaking sound is consequently heard, produced by its legs. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^um~u junodabK","text_ar":"اُمُّ جُنْدَبٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sand;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because the locust [or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jndb","text_ar":"جندب"},{"kind":"text","text":"] deposits its eggs therein: and the walker therein falls into evil [or encounters difficulty]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  [Hence it signifies also]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Misfortune:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perfidy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"faithlessness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"treachery:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wrong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"injury:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil conduct,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ill treatment."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqaEa fulaAnN fiY","text_ar":"وَقَعَ فُلَانٌ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^um~i junodabK","text_ar":"اُمِّ جُنْدَبٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one fell into misfortune:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into perfidy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqaEuwA fiY A^um~i junodabK","text_ar":"وَقَعُوا فِى اُمِّ جُنْدَبٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They suffered wrong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"injury."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqaEa Alqawomu junodabK","text_ar":"وَقَعَ القَوْمُ جُنْدَبٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"company of men, committed wrong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"injury, and slew him who was not a slayer:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [as though they came with violence upon sand in which eggs of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jndb","text_ar":"جندب"},{"kind":"text","text":"were deposited, and so destroyed the eggs, which had occasioned them no harm.] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakiba A^um~a junodabK","text_ar":"رَكِبَ اُمَّ جُنْدَبٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He committed wrong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"injury."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Sb","M","K","TA","MF","S"]},{"entry_id":"n6462","headword_ar":"جُنْدَبٌ","root":"jndb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junodubN","text_ar":"جُنْدُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janodabN","text_ar":"جَنْدَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jdb","text_ar":"جدب"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%AC%D9%86%D8%AF%D8%A8/","headword_ar":"جندب","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_49","lexicon_en":"Arabic-English Lexicon by Edward William Lane (d. 1876)","lexicon_ar":"المعجم العربي الإنجليزي لإدوارد وليام لين","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=10618#89e70e","body_html":"<h3>جندب</h3><br><br>جُنْدَبٌ and جُنْدُبٌ and جَنْدَبٌ: see art. جدب."},{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_3","lexicon_en":"Al-Khalīl b. Aḥmad al-Farāhīdī, Kitāb al-ʿAin (d. 786 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب العين للخليل بن أحمد الفراهيدي","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=10618#866e23","body_html":"<span>جندب: الجُندب: الذَّكرُ من الجراد، ويقال: يشبه الجراد.</span>"},{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_21","lexicon_en":"Muḥammad al-Fattinī, Majmaʿ Biḥār al-Anwār fī Gharāʾib al-Tanzīl wa Laṭāʾif al-Akhbār (d. 1578 CE)","lexicon_ar":"مجمع بحار الأنوار للفَتِّنيّ","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=10618#3ad46c","body_html":"<span class=\"title1\">[جندب]</span><span> فيه: فجعل \"الجنادب\" يقعن فيه، جمع جندب بضم دال وفتحها ضرب من الجراد، وقيل: هو الذي يصر في الحر. ومنه ح: كان يصلي الظهر و\"الجنادب\" تنقز من الرمضاء أي تثب.</span>"}]}}